snippet.title: Launch of LVM3-M4/CHANDRAYAAN-3 Mission from Satish Dhawan Space Centre (SDSC) SHAR, Sriharikota
snippet.description: Chandrayaan-3 is a follow-on mission to Chandrayaan-2 to demonstrate end-to-end capability in safe landing and roving on the lunar surface. It consists of Lander and Rover configuration. It will be launched by LVM3 from SDSC SHAR, Sriharikota. The propulsion module will carry the lander and rover configuration till 100 km lunar orbit. The propulsion module has Spectro-polarimetry of Habitable Planet Earth (SHAPE) payload to study the spectral and Polari metric measurements of Earth from the lunar orbit.

snippet.description:
Presenting Superhit Marathi Songs 2023 "Maval Jaga Zala Ra Official Song मावळ जागं झालं रं" from Marathi Movie "Subhedar". Beautifully Sung by Devdutta Manisha Baji , Avadhoot Gandhi and composed by Devdutta Manisha Baji. Lyrics penned by Digpal Lanjekar.

१८ ऑगस्टला गाजणार सिंहगडाचा पोवाडा.. 

सह्याद्रीला आज येतीया जाग, 
दख्खनचा गर्व ह्ये शिवाजी राजं.. 
सादर आहे सुभेदार मधील पहिलंवहिलं, आपल्या सर्वांचं गाणं 'मावळं जागं झालं रं..'!

Lyrics 
मावळं जागं झालं रं, तांबडं फुटलं भगवं जी..
गुलामी अंधार फिटं... सूर्य शिवबा उगवं जी..
मावळच्या मातीला जाग ही आली
तुमच्यापायी धरनी पावन जाली..
सह्याद्रीला आज येतीया जाग..
दख्खनचा गर्व ह्ये शिवाजी राजं..
हे सर्जा रं..
सोन्याच्या फाळानं शेतीची लेणी
कोरून काढी ह्यो मराठा मानी..
आधार जेयांचा मानी बळीराजं..
दख्खनचा गर्व ह्ये शिवाजी राजं..
शिवबा रं.. राजं रं.. मावळचं धनी
शिवबा राजं मर्दानी...
बिरुबा.. खंडुबा.. जोतिबा जो मनी
शिवबा तैसा मर्दानी..
काळाच्या ह्या.. भाळावरी
रेखियले भाग्य ऐसे तुम्ही..
जिजाईचा पुत्र असा
कनवाळू मायाळू राजं तुम्ही..
जीव प्रान वाहू पायी
संगती राहूया झुंजमंदी..
आशीर्वादे अंबाबाई..
शिवरायांना यश देई..
दुस्मन हा दबला हरला मावळा जितला तुमचा राजं
मावळ जागं झालं रं..
मराठा ऐसा तुमचा बुलंद गर्जे घुमला राजं..
मावळ जागं झालं रं..
मावळं जागं झालं रं, तांबडं फुटलं भगवं जी..
गुलामी अंधार फिटं सूर्य सिवबा उगवं जी..
शिवबा रं.. राजं रं.. मावळचं धनी
शिवबा राजं मर्दानी...
बिरुबा.. खंडुबा.. जोतिबा जो मनी
शिवबा तैसा मर्दानी..

full recipe:  https://hebbarskitchen.com/instant-idli-recipe-no-urad-dal-rice/

@hebbarskitchenhindi @hebbarskitchenoriginals 

Instant Idli Recipe | No Urad Dal Rice Flour Idli In 10 Mins with detailed photo and video recipe. An extremely simple and easy morning breakfast recipe prepared with rice flour and a small quantity of semolina. It is basically a quick or no-hassle idli recipe that does not require planning, soaking, grounding, or even fermentation. It is lite, and soft and more importantly takes only end-to-end 10 to 15 minutes to cook and serve for morning breakfast.


Instant Idli Recipe | No Urad Dal Rice Flour Idli In 10 Mins with step-by-step photo and video recipe. Instant recipes are always a popular choice, especially during the busy morning hour for the important breakfast meal. There are several instant recipes, but only a few of them are close to the traditional and authentic recipes. One such easy and simple instant recipe is the instant idli made with rice flour and served with a wide range of chutney recipes.

#hebbarskitchen

snippet.description:
The word “Implosion” is being surfaced in the news after the Titan incident. 
Implosion is a process in which objects are destroyed by collapsing (or being squeezed in) on themselves.
One reason behind the implosion of an object is the large  pressure difference between inside and outside the body. 

Here in this video, we are trying to demonstrate the process of implosion and thereby trying to educate our viewers about some topics such as the thermal expansion of water, atmospheric pressure and the process of implosion.

snippet.title: গোপাল কাজে দেরি করল কেন? | Gopal Bhar | Double Gopal | Full Episode
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to SONY AATH Channel: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCBz9qbqujcjIavFmBJW2oZw?sub_confirmation=1

Click to watch all the episodes of Gopal Bhar -
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL5O3zv2ZcASiKOTRSEBzEwxlnw10AkNbE

Episode 930 - 931: গোপাল কাজে দেরি করল কেন?
---------------------
Gopal, who is always on time, is late today, which surprises everyone at the Darbar. In the following episode, Montri gets a peculiar blue stain on his face that he fails to remove. Watch the show to find out why Gopal was late for work and how Montri managed to get rid of the blue color!

 About the show
-----------------------------
Gopal Bhar was a legendary court jester in medieval Bengal. He was in the court of Raja Krishnachandra, the famous king of Nadia in the 18th century AD. Such was the genius of Gopal that the King considered him a Navaratna of his court. His statue can still be seen in the palace of Raja Krishnachandra. Stories about his exploits are narrated in Bengal to this day and are immortalized in countless short stories. The stories are short, beautiful, humorous, and have a specific social message. Gopal Bhar is famous for stories of his wisdom, in which he outwits other fellow courtiers

snippet.title: ஆடி அமாவாசை 2023 - முன்னோர்கள் வழிபாடு, படையல் போடும் நேரம் & நாள்| Aadi Amavasai 17 June or 18 Aug?
snippet.description:
#Aadiamavasai #ஆடிஅமாவாசை #amavasya 

ஆடி அமாவாசை விரதம் ஆண்கள் எப்படி கடைப்பிடிக்க வேண்டும்? பெண்கள் எப்படி கடைப்பிடிக்க வேண்டும்? |Aadi Amavasai fasting | Aadi Amavasya
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WkwBLdcp-58

ஆடி அமாவாசை, பித்ரு தர்ப்பணம் கொடுக்க மிகச் சிறந்த நாள்.  அந்த அமாவாசை தினத்தில் நாம் செய்யும் தர்ப்பணத்தால், முன்னோர்களின் ஆசி நாம் பெறலாம். ‘நல்ல காரியங்கள் எல்லாவற்றையும் எள்ளும், தண்ணீரும் கொடுத்த பிறகே செய்யலாம்’ என்பது ஆன்றோர் வாக்கு. இது அமாவாசையில் தர்ப்பணம் செய்துவிட்டு தொடங்கும் காரியங்கள் வெற்றியாகவே முடியும் என்பதைக் குறிப்பதாகும்.

- ஆத்ம ஞான மையம் 

# ஆடி அமாவாசை 
# தர்ப்பணம் 
# சிரார்த்தம் 
# திதி 
# திவசம்
# தேச மங்கையர்க்கரசி 
# தேச மங்கையற்கரசி
# desa mangaiyarkarasi
# desamangayarkarasi
# desa mangayarkarasi
# athma gnana maiyam
# athmagnanamaiyam
# arivoli
# latest speech
# தேச மங்கையர்க்கரசி 
# தேசமங்கையற்கரசி 
# தேச மங்கையற்கரசி 
# ஆத்ம ஞான மையம் 
# ஆத்மஞானமையம் 
# அறிவொளி 
# Aadi amavasya

snippet.description:

#chandrayan3 #ISRO #chandrayan 

भारत ने श्रीहरिकोटा के सतीश धवन अंतरिक्ष केंद्र से चंद्रयान 3 मिशन को लॉन्च कर दिया है. क्या आपको पता है महज 4 दिन में चांद पर पहुंचा था अमेरिका...रुस को भी बस चार ही दिन लगे थे.लेकिन चंद्रयान 3 यानी भारत को चांद पर पहुंचने में लगेगे 42 दिन. आपको भी ये सोच कर आश्चर्य होगा कि Chandrayan 3  को चांद पर पहुंचने में आखिर इतना समय क्यों लग रहा है.जबकि अमेरिका- रुस जैसे देशो ने 50 साल पहले चांद की दूरी महज चार दिन में पूरी कर ली थी

snippet.title: Filmymoji || Middle Class Madhu || Something Missamma || Anjanam || Episode 02 || MCM
snippet.description:
Filmymoji Middle Class Madhu Something Missamma Anjanam Episode 02 MCM

Filmymoji releases its second episode of Something Missamma series, Anjanam, where after Middle class Madhu fell down from the bridge, Meku juttu Mahesh, Balli and Budatha gets very worried and run to their fathers seeking help. Everyone decided to file a complaint with the police. Police wants to cover up this incident because of the pressure from the local politician. 1A master advices them to get Anjanam, a very old mystical art of finding the lost people. Meanwhile at a far away checkpost in Rayalaseema, a police stops the lorry in which Middle class Madhu has fallen into. Watch the full episode to find out if 1A masters plan of finding Madhu through Anjanam works or whether police near the checkpost rescues Madhu from the lorry.

snippet.title: भारत जोड़ते किसान - धान की रोपाई, मंजी पर रोटी | Haryana Farmers | Rahul Gandhi
snippet.description:
किसानों का भारत को जोड़ने में बहुत बड़ा योगदान है - उनका उगाया हुआ अनाज देश की हर थाली का हिस्सा है, मगर उनकी इस तपस्या को सही फल और सम्मान नहीं मिलता।

भारत जोड़ो यात्रा अपने अगले चरण में सोनीपत, हरियाणा के खेतों में रुकी। मेरी मुलाकात दो किसान भाइयों, संजय मलिक और तसबीर कुमार से हुई। वो बचपन के जिगरी दोस्त हैं, जो कई सालों से एक साथ किसानी कर रहे हैं। जहां संजय जी ने ज़मीन सरकार से लीज़ पर ले रखी है, वही तसबीर जी उनके साथ 25% के ठेके पर काम करते हैं। उन्होंने बताया कि किसानी में हर पांच साल में से 3 साल मौसम के कारण नुकसान झेलना पड़ता है और ऐसी स्थिति में उन्हें सरकार की सहायता की ज़रूरत पड़ती है। 

पुरुष, महिलाएं, बच्चे, सभी खेतों में मौजूद थे - धान की रोपाई का खास दिन था। उनके साथ मिल कर खेतों में हाथ बटाया, ट्रैक्टर चलाया, धान बोया, दिल खोल कर कई बातें हुईं। महिलाओं ने घर की रोटियां खिलाई और अपने जीवन के बारे में बातचीत की। उनमें से किसी ने भी अब तक दिल्ली नहीं देखी थी। उन्होंने दिल्ली देखने की इच्छा जताई, और मुझे सब के साथ और वक़्त बिताने का मौक़ा मिला। 

सीधे-सादे, सच्चे और समझदार हैं भारत के किसान, अपने अधिकार भी पहचानते हैं। ज़रूरत आने पर काले कानूनों के खिलाफ़ डट जाते हैं तो साथ में MSP और बीमा की सही मांग भी उठाते हैं। अगर हम उन्हें सुने, उनकी बात समझें तो देश की कई समस्याएं सुलझ सकती हैं।
#rahulgandhi, #राहुल_गांधी, #bharatjodoyatra 

_

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

snippet.title: Ehraam-e-Junoon Episode 23 Teaser - 17th July 2023 - HAR PAL GEO
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Ehraam-e-Junoon Episode 23 Teaser - 17th July 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

"Ehraam-e-Junoon" follows the story of a young and immensely beautiful girl named Shanzay, who is filled with pride and stubbornness due to her upper-class upbringing. Shanzay believes that money can buy everything, including happiness. 

Despite her high standards, Shanzay is yet to find a man who can impress her until she meets Shayan at an event. Shayan is a handsome young man from a middle-class family, who takes up a job as a pizza delivery boy to make ends meet. Shanzay who is immediately drawn to Shayan wants to provide him with a better lifestyle however, Shayan keeps his distance and refuses to accept any of Shanzay’s advances.

As the story unfolds, Shanzay and Shayan's paths cross again and again, and Shanzay begins to question her beliefs about love and money. Will Shayan be the one to break through Shanzay's walls of pride and stubbornness, or will she continue to chase after superficial things?

The drama serial "Ehraam-e-Junoon" promises to take viewers on a rollercoaster ride of emotions as it explores the themes of love, pride, and class differences.

Writer: Jahanzeb Qamar
Director: Syed Ramish Rizvi
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi

snippet.title: Why does INDIA flood so easily? | Indian URBAN floods explained with solutions by Abhi and Niyu
snippet.description:
In this video, Abhi and Niyu discuss the reasons behind urban flooding in India. In July 2023, numerous places in India such as Delhi, Himachal, Uttarakhand, Punjab flooded after heavy rains. Climate change is making weather unpredictable for all of us. But did you know that floods have an economic impact as well? In this video we will discuss the economic impact of urban floods and how we can implement various solutions to solve this problem.

#floods #climatechange #abhiandniyu 

A video by Abhiraj Rajadhyaksha & Niyati Mavinkurve

The recent urban floods in India have caused widespread devastation, with millions of people affected. In Delhi, Himachal Pradesh, Punjab, and Uttarakhand, the floods have caused significant damage to infrastructure, businesses, and homes. The economic impact of these disasters is still being assessed, but it is clear that they will have a major impact on the country's economy.

In this video, we will discuss the economic impact of the urban floods in India. We will look at the damage that has been caused, the cost of the repairs, and the impact on the country's GDP. We will also discuss the steps that are being taken to mitigate the impact of future floods.

This video is important for anyone who is interested in the economic impact of natural disasters. It is also important for businesses and individuals who are affected by the floods. By understanding the economic impact of these disasters, we can better prepare for future floods and mitigate their damage.

About Us:
Abhi and Niyu is the fastest growing Indian educational YouTube channel. Abhi and Niyu are a husband-wife couple who believe in the power of our youth.

Abhi and Niyu started their page to talk about positive, impactful ideas and to inspire offline action from online content. It was a way to change the way our negative feeds operated and replace negative news with positive, action-oriented news that made some change. They decode and simplify issues for Millenials and believe small steps lead to big outcomes in the future. Their videos span different genres like history, environment, and sustainability, policy discussions, social commentary, economics, personal finance, among others.

Ehraam-e-Junoon Episode 22 - [Eng Sub] - Neelam Muneer - Imran Abbas - Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream - 17th July 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Ehraam-e-Junoon Digitally Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream

"Ehraam-e-Junoon" follows the story of a young and immensely beautiful girl named Shanzay, who is filled with pride and stubbornness due to her upper-class upbringing. Shanzay believes that money can buy everything, including happiness. 

Despite her high standards, Shanzay is yet to find a man who can impress her until she meets Shayan at an event. Shayan is a handsome young man from a middle-class family, who takes up a job as a pizza delivery boy to make ends meet. Shanzay who is immediately drawn to Shayan wants to provide him with a better lifestyle however, Shayan keeps his distance and refuses to accept any of Shanzay’s advances.

As the story unfolds, Shanzay and Shayan's paths cross again and again, and Shanzay begins to question her beliefs about love and money. Will Shayan be the one to break through Shanzay's walls of pride and stubbornness, or will she continue to chase after superficial things?

The drama serial "Ehraam-e-Junoon" promises to take viewers on a rollercoaster ride of emotions as it explores the themes of love, pride, and class differences.

Director: Syed Ramish Rizvi

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 3825 | 17 July 2023 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3825: Daya Ke Wapas Aane Ki News
--------------------------------------------------------
When Sundar found out about Jetha's second marriage, he became anxious. In order to get him to discuss about Daya's arrival, Jetha admits that the whole thing was a ruse. Finally, Daya's arrival time is revealed by Sundar, much to everyone's delight. Daya might not come right away because of the rites of the Sharavan month, but she will undoubtedly show up before Diwali. When they learn this news, all the people in Gokuldham feel relieved, but Jetha starts to have doubts. Sundar is questioned by Jetha on whether or not he is telling the truth. Sundar assures Jetha that he would never fabricate information regarding her sister. So, will Daya make a comeback during Diwali?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3825, 17 July 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo 

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Singer / performer: MC Stan ( Official baap )
Music Composer: MC Stan 
Author / Lyrics: MC Stan

Prod. by - MC STΔN

LYRICS: 
REGRET 

                   
                   “ HOOK “

Nai karta mein , apno mei game 
Likha maine itna , ki khatam hua pen ( pain )
Sab yaha pe , ajnabi the
Karma hota bro yaha pe , asliyat mei

Jisne mera , feel kara pain
Famous hone k liye , mera use karre name
Yeh bachkane bajrele , same
Dusre ki bala , tu khande pe le

                   ( VERSE - 1 )

Tension mei marela , cigarette 
Meko full horela , regret
Kaan mei tere , bola tha secret 
Teku mere baare mei , puchre

Angreez apne ko  , control karre door se
Log meko dekhte kyu , ghoor k 
Door rakho , ristheydaar door k
Mere dost , kaise kya bhool gaye ?

Sunnte chote bacche , meko school k
Generation haat mei , kaise bhool gaye
Kaante aate , gulaab k phool pe
Yeh gana likha , neend mei se uthke

Yeh rape karne wale , sab chuth gaye
Yeh rap karne wale sab , rukh gaye
Ladki k liye ghar , toot gaye
Mazil ka rasta nahi , puchte

                     “ HOOK “

Nai karta mein , apno mei game 
Likha mene itna , ki khatam hua pen
Sab yaha pe , ajnabi the
Karma hota bro yaha , asliyat mein

Jisne mera , feel kara pain
Famous hone k liye , mera use karre name
Yeh bachkane bajrele , same
Dusre ki bala , tu khande pe le

                  ( VERSE - 2 )

Chalna yeh log chahate , mere shoes mei
Likhela sab Cheeze , books mei
Mere ganne kaam aate , dukh mei
Tera bhai busy tha , shoot mei

Battya gul hogayele , mandal ke
Kabhi bhi mar sakta , sambhal k
Subhe jara uthte ja , fazar mei
Randomly pucha Maine , ek uncle se

Mere mom dad ne acche diye sanskaar , lekin yeh duniya ne meko heartless bana dali

Duniya ka kuch nahi , soch mat 4 log ka
Soch jo bhi pedi aage aane wali

Trust mera issue , meko trust pe bhi trust nahi hai
Insaan toh choti si baat aari 

Aaj bhi meko regret hota , maine kya kara kiske saat 
Raat ko nai neend aari …………💔

snippet.title: India successfully launches rocket for moon mission
snippet.description:
India's space agency launched a rocket on Friday that will attempt to land a spacecraft at the lunar south pole, an unprecedented feat that would advance the country's position as a significant space power. 
Subscribe to Guardian News on YouTube ► http://bit.ly/guardianwiressub

Television footage showed the Indian Space Research Organisation's launch rocket blast off from the country's main spaceport in the southern state of Andhra Pradesh, leaving behind a plume of smoke and fire. The Chandrayaan-3 mission is designed to deploy a lander and rover near the moon's south pole around 23 August.

Singer & Artist: Vikram Thakor
Artist: Kashish Rathore

Edit: Montu Rajput
Choreographer: Vishnu Thakor - Adalaj
Producer & Director: Gunvant Thakor
Music Label & Copyright: Jigar Studio

Lyrics Of This Song:
Jay Jay Dashama, Jay Jay Dashama
Darshan Dejo Maa, Jay Jay Dashamaa

Ho Moragadh Vali Maa, Pargat Paracha Vali Maa, Dashama Ni Aarti
Madi Kaljug Ma Gavani Maa, Navkhand Ma Pujani Maa, Dashama Ni Aarti
Ho Bhakto Tari Vat Juve Maa, Darshan Deva Aavajo
Aarti Na Ajvale Maa Velera Padharajo
Haa... Dhol Nagara Vage Maa, Zalar Na Rankare Maa, Dashama Ni Aarti
Ho Moragadh Vali Maa, Pargat Paracha Vali Maa, Dashama Ni Aarti

Ho Bholi Dashama Bhajiye Tane Ame Ghana Bhav Thi
Sankat Saghada Tali Jata Madi Tara Nam Thi
Ho... Ho Maa Dharya Kamo Karati Madi Daya Krupa Rakhati
Bhul Amari Thay To Madi Marag Tu Batavati
Ho Raiyat Ni Rakshak Maa Sandhaniye Asawar Jo
Hathma Kankan Chudala Shobhe Velera Padharajo
Ho Moragadh Vali Maa, Pargat Paracha Vali Maa, Dashama Ni Aarti
Maa Momaimaa Ni Aarati

Ho Dashmo Dhari Avatar Tu Kaliyug Ma Pragtani Maa
Dashe Dishaye Vas Tamaro Jagma Tu Pujani Maa
Ho... Ho... Ho... Hathe Trishul Shobhe Madi Sandhaniye Asawari Maa
 Haiya Na Hete Madi Murat Tari Sthapi Maa
Ho Jag Ni Tu Rakhevali Maa Ami Najaro Rakhajo
Akhand Jyot Tari Madi Velera Padharajo
Ho Moragadh Vali Maa, Pargat Paracha Vali Maa, Dashama Ni Aarti
Mari Momai Maa Ni Aarati

Ho Gher Gher Puja Tari Rakhopa Tara Nam Na
Samran Kari Puje Eni Puri Kare Manokamana
Ho Tane Na Visaray Madi Roj Bhave Bhajata
Gunvant Kahe Madi Tame Bhav Par Utarata
Ho Sau Koi Aave Dhame Tara Gunala Eto Gata Jo
Kanku Chokhaliye Fulade Madi Tane Sau Vadhave Jo
Ho Moragadh Vali Maa, Pargat Paracha Vali Maa, Dashama Ni Aarti
Mari Mavaladi Ni Aarati
Momaimani Aarti
Bolo Dashamat Ki... Jay....

snippet.title: Delhi Yamuna Flood: दिल्ली में घुसा यमुना का पानी, Ground Zero पर ये हाल ।Quint Hindi
snippet.description:
Delhi Floods Update: राजधानी दिल्ली में बाढ़ का खतरा लगातार बढ़ता ही जा रहा है. हथिनी कुंड बैराज से पानी छोड़े जाने के बाद दिल्ली में यमुना का जलस्तर 208.41 मीटर के पार पहुंच गया है. वहीं दिल्ली के निचले इलाकों में पानी भरने लगा है और सीएम अरविंद केजरीवाल ने भी लोगों से घर छोड़ने की अपील की है. इस बार यमुना के जल स्तर ने सारे रिकॉर्ड तोड़ दिए हैं. दिल्ली में लोगों ने शिविरों और फ्लाइओवर के नीचे आसरा लिया है. दिल्ली के कई वीवीआईपी इलाकों तक पानी पहुंच गया है. क्विंट हिंदी ने ग्राउंड पर पहुंच कर बेघर हुए लोगों से उनका हाल जाना.

#DelhiFlood #DelhiYamunaFlood #Delhi #Floods

snippet.title: TOFA - Seedhe Maut (Unmixed) | Prod. Hurricane
snippet.description:
!! NOT FROM LUNCHBREAK !!

Lyrics - 

Encore

Takatvar bole par taakat hai ni
Dil ke toote jazbaato se zaban maili
Hora hu apni parchai ka kaidi mai
Hu apne anjaam pe
Sahi me
Tabhi mai pehele jaha dekhta tha friends aur family 
Ab bas dikhta hai paisa aur eersha envy
Kya hai meri pehchaan?
“Ready made”
Hai vo yamraaj ki peheli bheint
Mai sweekaru khushi se
Khud ki khushi kargai khudakushi kabki mai 
Khush hu khuda ki aur  teri khushi me
Hum Cheeze dabake is seene me 
Maze le zindagi jeene me
Use bachao 
Dekhu jaha dikhe bas saanp with their fun out
Kuch waqt se hora tha andar se toxic
Khodu mai khudko 
Its time, get the gannd out
Mere aas paas hai jitni bhi bikhri hui zindagiya karta hu sabke liye jitna bhi kar kar pau
ek bache se poocha ki kya tere dil me vo bola dilli ko “dil walo ki banjao”

Hook 
Zindagi kya hai tofa 
Zindagi ya hai dhoka
Jaise tu dekhe

Zindagi kya hai dhoka 
Zindagi ya hai tofa
Jaise tu soch

Calm

Iss tofe ko le liya for granted 
Ab aadat ni sunne ki saath beth 
Bas aadat hai bolne ki my bad 
Aur inn laundo ko chahiye what calm has 

Bhai nahi hai perfect 

I Might’ve Deserved it 

Ab karu bas nashe 

Utara naqaab and im feeling the worst 

Utaari ye daaru firr utaara verse 

I followed my dream its a Blessing & curse 

 I can’t take it easy I got it 

Zindagi tofa jab yaar dost hai saath me

Jale J wagon r ude hawa me 

Zindagi tofa jab

Auro ki kahi suni kabhi suni hi na
Auro ki chali hui rahe chuni na
Chuna hai tujhe gar tu mujhe bhi kehede ki parwa hai tujhe meri to mai sehke is kandhe pe bhar kahunga fuck it ill make it

Hook 
Zindagi kya hai tofa 
Zindagi ya hai dhoka
Jaise tu dekhe

Zindagi kya hai dhoka 
Zindagi ya hai tofa
Jaise tu soch



Thanks Kyabc for the vid jaanemann XD

LUNCH BREAK COMING SOON.

snippet.title: OMG 2 - Official Teaser | Akshay Kumar, Pankaj Tripathi, Yami Gautam | Amit Rai | In Theatres Aug 11
snippet.description:
A sequel to the much celebrated OMG-Oh My God, OMG2 is a social comedy/drama starring Akshay Kumar, Pankaj Tripathi and Yami Gautam in lead roles. The film will release in theatres on August 11, 2023. 

Viacom18 Studio presents ​in association with Cape Of Good Films ​& Wakaoo Films 
A Cape Of Good Films and Wakaoo Films production ​
“OMG 2” 
Written & Directed by Amit Rai 
Produced by ​Aruna Bhatia, Cape Of Good Films 
Produced by ​Viacom18 Studios, Jyoti Deshpande, Ajit Andhare 
Produced by ​Swaroop Paresh Rawal, Hemal A. Thakkar​
Produced by ​Vipul D. Shah, Ashwin Varde, Rajesh Bahl
Creative Producer: Dr. Chandraprakash Dwivedi 
Co-Producer: Vedant Baali   
Story, Screenplay & Dialogues: Amit Rai 
Director Of Photography: Amalendu Chaudhary 
Music by Vikram Montrose, Hansraj Raghuwanshi, Djstrings, Pranaay, Sandesh Shandilya 
Lyrics by Shekhar Astitwa, Hansraj Raghuwanshi, Djstrings, Kabeer Shukla, Ginny Diwan, Sandesh Shandilya

राधाकृष्ण || RadhaKrishn Raasleela Part - 665 | Samb Ne Bheja Balram Ko Sandesh #radhakrishn #starbharat 

राधाकृष्ण || RadhaKrishn Raasleela Part - 665 | Samb Ne Bheja Balram Ko Sandesh #radhakrishn #starbharat 


►*About*
-------------
RadhaKrishn ke shaashwat prem ke vishay mein to sabhi ko gyaat hai. Radha bina Krishn nahin aur Krishn bina nahin Radha! Yadi Krishn Hriday hain, to Radha us hriday ki gati. Is premi yugal ki is mahagaatha mein aap jaanenge ki kis tarah Radha aur Krishn ne apne prem ko sansaar mein sthaapit kiya aur samast sansaar ko prem ki paribhasha sikhaayi, kyonki prem to bahut se log karte hain kintu keval prem ko paane ke liye… parantu RadhaKrishn ka prem ek-doosre ko paane ke liye nahin, apitu sansaar ko prem sikhaane ke liye tha. To dekhte rahiye RadhaKrishn ki ye anokhi prem-gaatha, jo Krishn nahin, apitu Radha ki drishti se likhee gayi hai!


#radhakrishn #starbharat #dildekedekhozara #mythology #राधाकृष्ण
#radhakrishna #sumallika #mallikasingh #radha

snippet.title: Chandrayaan 3 Complete Story
snippet.description:
Angel One Demat Account(Free) - https://tinyurl.com/2f32osnb
For support, WhatsApp 8688962057

Chandrayaan-3 is a planned third lunar exploration mission by the Indian Space Research Organisation (ISRO). It will consist of a lander and a rover similar to Chandrayaan-2, but would not have an orbiter. Its propulsion module will behave like a communication relay satellite. The propulsion module will carry the lander and rover configuration until the spacecraft is in a 100 km lunar orbit.

Following Chandrayaan-2, where a last-minute software glitch in the soft landing guidance software led to the failure of the lander's soft landing attempt after a successful orbital insertion, another lunar mission was proposed.

The launch of Chandrayaan-3 has been scheduled for July 14, 2023, at 2:35 pm IST.

Bojh Episode 75 - [Eng Sub] - Areej Mohyudin - Fahad Sheikh - Sana Fakhar - 17th July 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

The drama serial revolves around the lives of a contented and loving family of Ashfaq and Sonia, along with their children Amal and Rafay. Amal, the elder daughter, is a student pursuing her undergraduate degree. She harbours a secret love for one of her classmates, Shazim, who belongs to an affluent and powerful family. However, Amal has never expressed her feelings to anyone.

On the other hand, Rehan, a fellow classmate of Amal, is secretively in love with her but hides his feelings due to his middle-class background and financial struggles. The plot takes a tragic turn when Amal's father, Ashfaq, is arrested on false corruption charges, leaving the family penniless and at the mercy of others. The family's once comfortable and happy life is turned upside down, and they are forced to face the harsh realities of life.

The drama is a heart-wrenching tale of love, loss, and survival as the family tries to cope with their new reality. Will Amal be able to find a way to support herself and her family? Despite Rehan’s financial constraints, will he be able to help Amal for the sake of his love?

►*About*
-------------
RadhaKrishn ke shaashwat prem ke vishay mein to sabhi ko gyaat hai. Radha bina Krishn nahin aur Krishn bina nahin Radha! Yadi Krishn Hriday hain, to Radha us hriday ki gati. Is premi yugal ki is mahagaatha mein aap jaanenge ki kis tarah Radha aur Krishn ne apne prem ko sansaar mein sthaapit kiya aur samast sansaar ko prem ki paribhasha sikhaayi, kyonki prem to bahut se log karte hain kintu keval prem ko paane ke liye… parantu RadhaKrishn ka prem ek-doosre ko paane ke liye nahin, apitu sansaar ko prem sikhaane ke liye tha. To dekhte rahiye RadhaKrishn ki ye anokhi prem-gaatha, jo Krishn nahin, apitu Radha ki drishti se likhee gayi hai!

Lyrics:
humne kiye aise sawal
jinka mila na jawab unse

toot gaya mera jahaan
jisko dhaage se banaya bunke

ajnabi huye wo jo kabhi the apne 
aye na fir kabhi milne /mudke vo hum rishte kya hi rakhte

na-dani, na-samjhi unki ya kuch bhi kehlo
humko bin kahe alvida

wo hue laapata
ab dhoondhein kahan hum
unke nisha
wo hue laapata
na duri kate - hain darmiyaan

ab har ek aayine mein tera hi aks hai
tera ruthke chale jana kyu bada bewaqt hai

tera chehra nigaahon mein kuch aise rakhke chala hun
mukhtasar na bhi ho manzil , main tera banke raha hu..

tum kahi dur…
chale gaye ho, ye kyu hua hai

mujhko chur…..
kar chale / chuke ho, ye sab kya hai

wo hue laapata
dhoondhein kahan hum
unke nisha
wo hue laapata
na duri kate hain darmiyaan

ajnabi huye wo jo kabhi the apne 
aye na fir kabhi milne vo hum rishte kya hi rakte

na-dani , na-samjhi unki ya kuch bhi kehlo
humko bin kahe alvida

wo hue laapata

snippet.title: PUBG Love Story : प्यार की ख़ातिर Pakistan से भारत आईं Seema ज़मानत के बाद क्या-क्या बोलीं? (BBC)
snippet.description:
भारत के ग्रेटर नोएडा में रहने वाले सचिन मीणा से प्यार करने वालीं सीमा का कहना है कि वो कभी भी लौटकर पाकिस्तान नहीं जाना चाहतीं. कराची की रहने वाली सीमा पहले शारजाह के रास्ते नेपाल पहुंचीं और नेपाल से भारत में आकर रहने लगी थीं. उन दोनों को पुलिस ने हिरासत में ले लिया था, लेकिन ज़मानत मिलने के बाद उन लोगों ने मीडिया से बातचीत की. बीबीसी टीम ने जब दोनों से मुलाकात की तो दोनों का कहना था कि सीमा लौटकर पाकिस्तान नहीं जाना चाहती. शऊदी अरब में रहने वाले सीमा के पति गुलाम हैदर ने सीमा और सचिन के बारे में काफ़ी कुछ कहा था, उस पर भी सीमा ने जवाब दिया है.

वीडियो: अभिनव गोयल और शाहनवाज़ अहमद

 #Pakistan #PUBG #indiapakistanlovestory 

सीमा हैदर के गले में 'राधे-राधे' का दुपट्टा और मंगलसूत्र, सचिन के घर में गूंजते 'जय श्री राम' के नारे- ग्राउंड रिपोर्ट
https://www.bbc.com/hindi/articles/ce9kzvgqgw6o

वो ‘ग़लती’ जिससे पकड़ी गईं पाकिस्तान की सीमा ग़ुलाम हैदर
https://www.bbc.com/hindi/articles/c3gz68559z3o

सचिन के लिए लांघी भारत-पाक सरहद, सलाखों के पीछे कैसे पहुंचीं सीमा गुलाम हैदर
https://www.bbc.com/hindi/articles/crgdgwq4zzgo
https://youtu.be/wLRau6G40BE

* ऐसे ही और दिलचस्प वीडियो देखने के लिए चैनल सब्सक्राइब ज़रूर करें-
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCN7B-QD0Qgn2boVH5Q0pOWg?disable_polymer=true

* बीबीसी हिंदी से आप इन सोशल मीडिया चैनल्स पर भी जुड़ सकते हैं-

फ़ेसबुक- https://www.facebook.com/BBCnewsHindi
ट्विटर- https://twitter.com/BBCHindi
इंस्टाग्राम- https://www.instagram.com/bbchindi/
